Command Pattern wraps all the requests into one single object as a command
and pass it to the invoker class.In command pattern the commands use the same interface
so as to have the requests from the same sender

In the ButtonOperation package:
     AddCommand
                        : are the command classes that implements Command interface
     SubtractCommand

     CommandMainClass   : in the main class

     RequestCollection  : is the class that manages all the requests.It is the
                          invoker class.

     ButtonOperations   : is the logic class.In this package it is addition
                          and subtraction logic.

     Command            : is the interface class.

